    • Method Detail

      • list

        public CompatibilityReleases.ListInvocation list(java.lang.String host)
        Description copied from interface: CompatibilityReleases
        Lists the locally available ESXi releases for a given host that can be used to generate a compatiblity report. Each host has its own list of supported releases depending on its current release.

        Invocation Result:
        Available releases for compatibility for a specified host.

        Specified by:
        list in interface CompatibilityReleases
        Parameters:
        host - Contains the MoID identifying the ESXi host. The parameter must be an identifier for the resource type: HostSystem.
        Returns:
        instance of CompatibilityReleases.ListInvocation which upon invoke executes the above described list operation. The operation result or the operation error will be stored in the CompletionStageFuture that invoke returns.
